snippet.title: Liquidator: 3D Action - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Part of my Obscure First Person Shooters series: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2BBA1AB1CF53EEAC

Gameplay footage from Liquidator. It appears to be a Russian game made on the Build engine.

I honestly have no idea what is going on. I really don't. In fact, this entire experience has been deeply upsetting. I'm just going to lie down and weep softly for a while.
